## 4. BACKEND ‚Äî DEEP DIVE

### 4.1 Startup & Entry Points

There are **two separate FastAPI applications** in this project:

| Entry Point | File | Port | Used By |
|---|---|---|---|
| `python start_server_v3.py` | [backend/main.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/main.py) (814 lines) | **8002** | **PRODUCTION** ‚Äî Extension + Dashboard |
| `python -m app.main` | [backend/app/main.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/app/main.py) (40 lines) | 8000 | Legacy modular version (NOT actively used) |

**[start_server_v3.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/start_server_v3.py)** is the main entry:
```python
uvicorn.run("backend.main:app", host="0.0.0.0", port=8002, reload=True, reload_dirs=[PROJECT_ROOT])
```

### 4.2 The Primary Backend ([backend/main.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/main.py) ‚Äî 814 lines)

This is a **monolithic** FastAPI application containing most endpoints inline. Key characteristics:

#### ML Model Loading (CURRENTLY DISABLED)
```python
model = None
vectorizer = None
MODEL_STATUS = "DISABLED (Code Safety)"
# CRITICAL: Sklearn model is causing Segfaults on load.
# We are disabling it completely to ensure backend stability.
```

The enhanced model ([model_enhanced.joblib](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/models/model_enhanced.joblib), 33MB SGD Classifier) was trained on ~1.1M samples but **causes segfaults** when loaded via `joblib.load()`. The system currently operates in **STRICT BLOCKLIST + HEURISTIC MODE** without the ML model.

#### Detection Pipeline (POST `/api/v1/detect`)

The main detection endpoint processes URLs through this cascade:

```
1. Input Validation
   ‚îî‚îÄ Skip empty, text content, localhost
2. Domain Normalization (normalize_domain)
3. User Blocklist Check (DB: blocked_domains)
   ‚îî‚îÄ Returns risk=1.0, level=Critical
4. User Whitelist Check (DB: allowed_domains)
   ‚îî‚îÄ Returns risk=0.0, level=Low
5. Built-in Whitelist (~80 domains)
   ‚îî‚îÄ Google, YouTube, Amazon, Wikipedia, etc.
   ‚îî‚îÄ Returns risk=0.0, level=Low
6. STRICT Keyword Blacklist (~70 keywords)
   ‚îî‚îÄ Adult, piracy, crack, torrent, crypto, etc.
   ‚îî‚îÄ Returns risk=0.88, level=High
7. Suspicious Keyword Check (~15 keywords)
   ‚îî‚îÄ Gambling, deepfake, payday loan
   ‚îî‚îÄ Returns risk=0.70, level=Medium
8. Heuristic Analysis
   ‚îî‚îÄ IP address in URL? (+0.3)
   ‚îî‚îÄ URL length > 75? (+0.3)
   ‚îî‚îÄ Suspicious chars (@, - in domain)? (+0.2)
9. ML Model Inference (IF model loaded‚Äîcurrently skipped)
   ‚îî‚îÄ SGD predict_proba ‚Üí confidence score
10. Advanced Analysis
    ‚îî‚îÄ Baseline "Alive" Factor (subdomain depth, query params, entropy jitter)
    ‚îî‚îÄ LLM Verification (Gemini, for ambiguous sites 0.05‚Äì0.6)
11. Final Decision
    ‚îî‚îÄ >0.95 ‚Üí Critical
    ‚îî‚îÄ >0.85 ‚Üí High
    ‚îî‚îÄ ‚â•0.35 ‚Üí Medium
    ‚îî‚îÄ else ‚Üí Low
12. Persist to SQLite (scan_results table)
```

