### 4.5 Services Layer

#### LlmService ([backend/app/services/llm.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/app/services/llm.py))
- **LLM Provider**: Google Gemini (`google-generativeai`)
- **Model**: `models/gemini-flash-latest`
- **API Key**: Loaded from [.env.local](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/.env.local) ‚Üí `GEMINI_API_KEY`
- **Two functions**:
  1. [chat_with_context(message, context)](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/app/services/llm.py#60-138) ‚Äî AI chatbot, returns `{response, suggestions[]}`
  2. [analyze_url(url)](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/app/services/llm.py#139-179) ‚Äî URL safety analysis, returns `{confidence, signals[]}`
- **Fallback**: Returns `confidence: 0.8` (mostly safe) if LLM fails
- **Rate limit handling**: Rotates through model list with 1s backoff

#### InferenceService ([backend/app/services/inference.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/app/services/inference.py))
- **Model**: [model_baseline.joblib](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/models/model_baseline.joblib) (LogisticRegression, OneVsRest)
- **Vectorizer**: [vectorizer_baseline.joblib](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/models/vectorizer_baseline.joblib) (TF-IDF, 5000 features)
- **Labels**: `['urgency', 'authority', 'fear', 'impersonation']`
- **Output**: Multi-label probability predictions + top contributing features
- **Used by**: `/api/v1/analyze` route (modular app only)

#### Impersonation Service ([backend/app/services/impersonation.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/app/services/impersonation.py))
- **Typosquatting Detection**: Uses `difflib.SequenceMatcher` with 0.85 similarity threshold
- **Protected Entities**: PayPal, Google, Microsoft, Facebook, Apple, Amazon, Netflix, LinkedIn, Dropbox, Adobe, Bank of America, Chase, Wells Fargo
- **Entity Mismatch**: Checks if page title claims an entity but domain doesn't match
- **Returns**: [(risk_score_addition, warning_message)](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/my-app/app/page.tsx#5-18)

#### Temporal Service ([backend/app/services/temporal.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/app/services/temporal.py))
- **Late Night** (23:00‚Äì05:00): +0.2 risk multiplier
- **Friday Afternoon** (16:00‚Äì20:00): +0.15 risk multiplier  
- **Weekend** (Sat/Sun): +0.1 risk multiplier

#### Telemetry Service ([backend/app/services/telemetry.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/app/services/telemetry.py))
- **Purpose**: Generate fake "shadow" scan data to keep dashboard alive during demos
- **Status**: **DISABLED** by user request
- **When active**: Creates 1-3 random scan events every 15-30 seconds

