## 8. KNOWN ISSUES & TECHNICAL DEBT

### 8.1 Critical Issues

| Issue | Impact | Location |
|---|---|---|
| **ML model disabled** ‚Äî Enhanced model segfaults on `joblib.load()` | System runs without ML, relying only on keyword lists and LLM | `backend/main.py:64-74` |
| **Missing temporal router** ‚Äî `from app.routes import temporal` fails (file deleted) | Backend crashes on startup | `backend/main.py:651` (FIXED ‚Äî commented out) |
| **Duplicate FastAPI apps** ‚Äî Two separate apps with overlapping routes | Confusion, potential port mismatch bugs | [backend/main.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/main.py) vs [backend/app/main.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/app/main.py) |
| **Stale port in api.ts** ‚Äî Defaults to port 8000 instead of 8002 | [analyzeMessage()](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/my-app/lib/api.ts#5-21) function fails | `my-app/lib/api.ts:3` |
| **Turbopack cache corruption** ‚Äî `.next/` cache gets corrupted regularly | Frontend crashes on fresh start with panic error | [my-app/package.json](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/my-app/package.json) (FIXED ‚Äî auto-clears `.next/` on dev) |

### 8.2 Architecture Issues

| Issue | Description |
|---|---|
| **Monolithic backend** | [backend/main.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/main.py) is 814 lines with all endpoints inline, while a modular version exists but isn't used |
| **PyTorch imported but unused** | `import torch` in main.py but no PyTorch models are used (wasted startup time + dependency) |
| **Random jitter in risk scores** | `random.uniform(0.01, 0.04)` added to every score makes results non-deterministic |
| **Duplicate route definitions** | `/api/v1/block`, `/api/v1/unblock`, `/api/v1/blocklist`, `/api/v1/privacy/settings` defined both inline and in routers |
| **Two databases** | [sql_app.db](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/sql_app.db) (main) and `sentinel.db` (events) with different schemas |
| **No authentication** | All endpoints are publicly accessible, no user sessions |
| **Extension pulls every 4 seconds** | Blocklist sync interval is very aggressive, could be 30-60s |
| **Hardcoded benign domains** | ~80 domains hardcoded as safe; should be in DB or config file |
| **`POST /api/v1/privacy/settings` defined 3 times** | Three handler functions for the same route in [backend/main.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/backend/main.py) |

### 8.3 ML/AI Issues

| Issue | Description |
|---|---|
| **No model serving** | The trained 33MB model can't load due to segfault |
| **Labels are wrong for URL-only analysis** | Model labels (urgency, authority, fear, impersonation) are designed for text content analysis, not URL-only detection |
| **HashingVectorizer not saved** | Enhanced vectorizer file is only 396 bytes because `HashingVectorizer` is stateless (by design) ‚Äî but this means manual features also need to be reconstructed |
| **Hard negatives may be stale** | `hard_negatives.csv` generated once; no automated retraining pipeline |
| **Gemini fallback defaults to "safe"** | If LLM fails, returns `confidence: 0.8` (mostly safe), potentially missing threats |
| **No model evaluation metrics logged** | No confusion matrix, precision/recall, or F1 scores stored |

