## 12. IMPROVEMENT OPPORTUNITIES

### High Priority
1. **Fix ML model loading** ‚Äî Either fix the segfault issue, retrain with a compatible sklearn version, or switch to ONNX Runtime for serving
2. **Consolidate to one FastAPI app** ‚Äî Merge the modular router structure into the main app, eliminate duplicate endpoints
3. **Remove unused PyTorch import** ‚Äî Saves ~2s startup time and eliminates CUDA detection overhead
4. **Add authentication** ‚Äî JWT or session-based auth for the dashboard
5. **Fix port mismatch in [lib/api.ts](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/my-app/lib/api.ts)** ‚Äî Change default from 8000 to 8002

### Medium Priority
6. **Move hardcoded lists to database/config** ‚Äî Benign domains, strict keywords, and suspicious keywords should be configurable
7. **Add proper error handling** ‚Äî Many `except Exception: pass` blocks silently swallow errors
8. **Implement model retraining pipeline** ‚Äî Automated retraining from accumulated scan data
9. **Add rate limiting** ‚Äî The extension polls aggressively; backend should have rate limits
10. **WebSocket for real-time updates** ‚Äî Replace polling with WebSocket connections

### Low Priority
11. **Add end-to-end tests** ‚Äî No test files exist in the project
12. **Docker containerization** ‚Äî Package backend + frontend for easy deployment
13. **Implement the transformer model** ‚Äî [train_transformers.py](file:///d:/coding_files/Projects/DTLshit/scripts/train_transformers.py) exists as placeholder
14. **Add user management** ‚Äî Multi-user support with separate blocklists/settings
15. **Reduce extension blocklist polling** ‚Äî 4s ‚Üí 30-60s with WebSocket push for changes
